NB. =========================================================
NB. pdf_circle
NB.
NB. returns bezier points to draw circle
NB. with given center and radius
NB.
NB. result is 4 row table, each row being a 90 degree arc.
pdf_circle=: 3 : 0
'x y r'=. y
arc=. _2 [\ 0 1 2 1 1 2 1 0 { 0 1, 4r3*<:%:2
arr=. |."1 arc *"1 [ _1 1
mat=. _4 ,\ arc,arr,-arc,arr
(mat * r) + ($mat) $ x,y
)


